title: Exception Thrown When Exporting Data in Table Within a Grid Cell
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table that is located inside a grid cell.
EB: The expected behavior is that data from tables within grid cells can be exported without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Insert a table into one grid cell.
2. Insert another table into a different grid cell.
3. Attempt to export data from one of the tables within a grid cell, which will trigger the exception.
